# n8n TickTick Autoscheduler — credentials reference
#
# This file is a TEMPLATE. Copy it to `.env` (which is gitignored) and fill in
# the real values. These secrets are NOT consumed automatically by anything in
# this repo — they live here so you have one canonical local record of what
# you pasted into n8n's credential store.
#
# Where each value is used:
#  - GOOGLE_OAUTH_*  -> n8n credential of type "Google Calendar OAuth2 API"
#                      (used by the "Get Busy slots" node)
#  - TICKTICK_*      -> n8n credential of type "HTTP Bearer Auth"
#                      (used by the "Query TickTick projects/tasks" and
#                       "Write back TickTick tasks" nodes)

# --- Google Cloud OAuth client ---
# Source: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# Project: n8n-calendar (organization: ebikeee.com)
GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET=

# --- TickTick OAuth app + Bearer token ---
# Source: https://developer.ticktick.com/manage
# The Bearer token is what gets pasted into the n8n credential.
# It is obtained by running the OAuth2 authorization code flow against
# https://ticktick.com/oauth/authorize with scope=tasks:read tasks:write
TICKTICK_CLIENT_ID=
TICKTICK_CLIENT_SECRET=
TICKTICK_ACCESS_TOKEN=
